18:28.441 --> 18:29.609
What is it?

18:30.235 --> 18:31.069
There's blood!

18:31.194 --> 18:32.612
- Hey!
- That guy!

18:32.737 --> 18:33.613
Ryo.

18:34.405 --> 18:36.991
Both Black Mass
and Sabbath come with blood.

18:39.160 --> 18:39.953
Blood.

18:40.078 --> 18:42.330
Blood! Blood!

18:48.044 --> 18:50.463
Stop! Ryo, stop it!

18:50.588 --> 18:53.258
They're all scum anyway.
There's no need to be sad.

18:53.633 --> 18:54.843
You're scum, too!

18:57.929 --> 18:59.430
- Ryo!
- You, too!

19:08.398 --> 19:11.901
You want to touch my boobs?
Look behind you.

19:12.527 --> 19:13.820
Take that!

19:56.696 --> 19:57.530
It started.

20:06.331 --> 20:07.582
No.

20:07.916 --> 20:09.083
Help me!

20:10.043 --> 20:11.002
But...

20:37.820 --> 20:39.781
Amon. Now's your chance.

20:39.906 --> 20:41.699
Possess Akira. Amon.

21:16.442 --> 21:17.068
Ryo!

21:21.864 --> 21:23.700
<i>Why do you run?</i>

21:23.825 --> 21:27.161
<i>Your physical ability is nothing,
compared to even cats and dogs.</i>

21:27.787 --> 21:29.622
<i>You would get eaten by a devil.</i>

21:29.747 --> 21:31.791
<i>Eaten... Eaten...</i>

21:31.916 --> 21:34.252
<i>Eaten... Eaten...</i>

22:19.213 --> 22:19.881
Amon?

22:20.006 --> 22:21.382
Amon?

22:46.157 --> 22:50.536
<i>I've made Akira into a devil.</i>

22:52.705 --> 22:53.664
<i>And...</i>

22:54.457 --> 23:00.922
<i>I might have created the most powerful,
ruthless, and brutal devil in this world.</i>

